Hello beauties ❤️ Here's a quick acne cover up mini tutorial that a lot of you requested #mayabeaute 💕 follow me on snap chat 👻 maya.beauty طريقة تغطية الحبوب اللي كتير منكم سألني عنا، إنشاءالله يفيدكم، تابعوني ع السناب 👻maya.beauty ❤️
Acne Cover-up:
Some deeply pigmented acne scars need a little more work to conceal as the pigmentation may still be visible after concealing using the traditional way, layering is the way to go with more pigmentation:
1. @lagirlcosmetics green concealer
2. @makeupforever hd concealer
3. @lagirlcosmetics orange concealer
3. foundation from @makeupforeveroffical ultra HD
4. loose powder
@mayabeautestudios

Signature deep cleansing facial with @mayabeaute @mayabeautestudios- this is kinda like your semi-annual teeth cleaning, except that it's for your skin 😆 - that's the way I like to describe it to my clients. It's important to get a deep cleansing facial from time to time in order to remove the dirt, sebum, and dead skin build up from the skin. This is only a tiny part of the facial, I follow through with properly closing the pores and balancing the skin's PH level, and hydrating it ❤️ We are located in Northern California, in Campbell, for bookings contact support@mayabeaute.com or call +14088216165 @mayabeautestudios
